-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
extern/assignmentoptimal is obtained from
http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/6543.  The
compiled mex file is copied to the folder +braidlab/private. (Version
2011-07-05)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
extern/VariablePrecisionIntegers is obtained from
http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/22725-variable-precision-integer-arithmetic.
The functions not used by braidlab are not included. (Version 31 Jul
2013)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
extern/CBraid is checked out from https://github.com/jeanluct/cbraid
in a separate branch cbraid-branch.  To update CBraid to the latest:
  git checkout cbraid-branch; git pull # pull changes from remote cbraid-remote
  git checkout develop
  git merge --squash -Xsubtree=extern/cbraid --no-commit cbraid-branch
(http://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Advanced-Merging, "Subtree Merging")

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
extern/trains is checked out from https://github.com/jeanluct/trains
in a separate branch trains-branch.  To update trains to the latest:
  git checkout trains-branch; git pull # pull changes from remote trains-remote
  git checkout develop
  git merge --squash -Xsubtree=extern/trains --no-commit trains-branch
(http://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Advanced-Merging, "Subtree Merging")
